attributes.description: Tata Investment Corporation Ltd is primarily engaged in the business of investment in listed and unlisted equity shares, debt instruments and mutual funds etc. of companies in a wide range of industries. The company is a NBFC registered with the RBI under the category of Investment Company.[1]
